'''Black Rhinos FC''' is a [[Zimbabwean]] [[soccer|football]] club based in [[Harare]]. They currently play in the top division in Zimbabwean Football. Their home stadium is the [[Akii-Bua Stadium]].

Black Rhinos were promoted to the top level of Zimbabwean football, the [[Zimbabwe Premier Soccer League]], after they were champions of the Northern Division of the Second Level during the 1997 season.<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesz/zimb97.html Zimbabwe 1997<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>
